10:04.304 --> 10:05.271
THIS GRITTY NEIGHBORHOOD RIGHT

10:05.271 --> 10:06.773
ON THE EDGE OF MANILA.

10:06.773 --> 10:08.641
IT'S A PLACE WHERE FAMILIES

10:08.641 --> 10:09.576
STRUGGLE TO GET BY ON ONE OR TWO

10:09.576 --> 10:12.178
DOLLARS A DAY AT BEST.

10:12.178 --> 10:13.813
HERE VERY YOUNG CHILDREN

10:13.813 --> 10:16.015
SCAVENGE THROUGH GARBAGE IN

10:16.015 --> 10:17.217
SEARCH OF SOMETHING TO SELL FOR

10:17.217 --> 10:18.418
A FEW DOLLARS TO HELP SUPPORT

10:18.418 --> 10:21.221
THEIR FAMILIES.

10:21.221 --> 10:24.290
FAMILIES IN ASIA'S MOST CATHOLIC

10:24.290 --> 10:25.792
COUNTRY THAT HAVE HAD LITTLE OR

10:25.792 --> 10:28.027
NO ACCESS TO CONTRACEPTION OR

10:28.027 --> 10:29.863
FAMILY PLANNING ADVICE--

10:29.863 --> 10:31.931
FAMILIES THAT OFTEN GET LARGER

10:31.931 --> 10:33.266
BY THE YEAR.

10:33.266 --> 10:38.204
VILMA LOPEZ HAS TEN CHILDREN,

10:38.204 --> 10:38.805
AGES ONE TO 20.

10:38.805 --> 10:41.841
SHE HAD HER FIRST CHILD AT 19.

10:41.841 --> 10:42.675
>> WE DIDN'T PLAN IT, IT JUST

10:42.675 --> 10:44.043
HAPPENED EVERY YEAR.

10:44.043 --> 10:45.745
IT'S JUST EASY FOR ME TO GET

10:45.745 --> 10:47.447
PREGNANT.

10:47.447 --> 10:48.615
>> Reporter: MANILA IS NOW ONE

10:48.615 --> 10:50.216
OF THE MOST DENSELY POPULATED

10:50.216 --> 10:51.784
URBAN AREA ON EARTH-- SO

10:51.784 --> 10:54.420
CONGESTED, SOME ARE FORCED TO

10:54.420 --> 10:56.856
SEEK REFUGE IN LOCAL CEMETERIES,

10:56.856 --> 10:58.625
WHERE THEY EAT AND SLEEP ON

10:58.625 --> 11:03.730
TOMBS AND MAUSOLEUMS.

11:03.730 --> 11:04.831
>> IN THE PHILIPPINES, THERE IS

11:04.831 --> 11:06.599
FAMILY PLANNING, BUT IT IS

11:06.599 --> 11:08.301
AVAILABLE ONLY TO THE RICH, TO

11:08.301 --> 11:09.502
THOSE WHO ARE ABLE TO AFFORD TO

11:09.502 --> 11:11.538
GO SEE DOCTORS, TO BUY PILLS.

11:11.538 --> 11:15.008
>> Reporter: ESPERANZA CABRAL, A

11:15.008 --> 11:16.776
FORMER HEALTH SECRETARY OF THE

11:16.776 --> 11:18.478
PHILIPPINES, HAS BEEN SOUNDING

11:18.478 --> 11:21.147
THE ALARM ON THE POPULATION

11:21.147 --> 11:23.616
CRISIS HERE, A POPULATION

11:23.616 --> 11:25.785
GROWING FASTEST AMONG THE

11:25.785 --> 11:27.487
POOREST FILIPINOS, THOSE WHOSE

11:27.487 --> 11:28.588
NEED FOR BIRTH CONTROL IS THE

11:28.588 --> 11:31.424
GREATEST.

11:31.424 --> 11:34.260
>> FOR THE POOR AMONG US, IT IS

11:34.260 --> 11:37.430
OFTEN AN ASPIRATION, SOMETHING

11:37.430 --> 11:38.531
THEY WANT TO DO BUT ARE NOT ABLE

11:38.531 --> 11:40.266
TO DO.

11:40.266 --> 11:41.935
>> Reporter: DR. SILVIA DE LA

11:41.935 --> 11:42.936
PAZ SAYS TEEN PREGNANCIES ARE AT

11:42.936 --> 11:44.270
AN ALL-TIME HIGH.

11:44.270 --> 11:45.338
>> WITH THE LACK OF

11:45.338 --> 11:46.272
CONTRACEPTIVES, SO WHAT ELSE

11:46.272 --> 11:47.473
WILL THEY DO?

11:47.473 --> 11:48.575
HAVE BABIES-- MORE AND MORE

11:48.575 --> 11:49.842
BABIES, YOU KNOW.

11:49.842 --> 11:53.713
SO IT'S A SAD PICTURE.

11:53.713 --> 11:55.014
>> Reporter: FOR YEARS THE U.N.

11:55.014 --> 11:57.817
HAS URGED THE PHILIPPINE

11:57.817 --> 11:58.985
GOVERNMENT TO TAKE ACTION, TO

11:58.985 --> 12:00.286
PROVIDE FREE CONTRACEPTION AND

12:00.286 --> 12:02.956
FAMILY PLANNING FOR THE POOR.

12:02.956 --> 12:03.990
RECENT SURVEYS INDICATE EIGHT IN

12:03.990 --> 12:09.696
TEN FILIPINOS NOW AGREE.

12:09.696 --> 12:12.365
BUT THE PHILIPPINES' MOST

12:12.365 --> 12:13.733
POWERFUL INSTITUTION, THE ROMAN

12:13.733 --> 12:15.969
CATHOLIC CHURCH, HAS FOUGHT

12:15.969 --> 12:16.970
FAMILY PLANNING POLICIES EVERY

12:16.970 --> 12:19.772
TIME THEY ARE RAISED.

12:19.772 --> 12:21.074
IN A COUNTRY WHERE MORE THAN 80%

12:21.074 --> 12:22.408
ARE PRACTICING CATHOLICS, THE

12:22.408 --> 12:24.944
CHURCH HAS DOMINATED NEARLY

12:24.944 --> 12:27.847
EVERY ASPECT OF LIFE IN THE

12:27.847 --> 12:29.549
PHILIPPINES FOR MORE THAN 400

12:29.549 --> 12:31.150
YEARS, IT'S MORAL AUTHORITY AND

12:31.150 --> 12:32.685
POLITICAL POWER RARELY

12:32.685 --> 12:33.653
CHALLENGED, ESPECIALLY WHEN IT

12:33.653 --> 12:37.357
COMES TO REPRODUCTION.

12:37.357 --> 12:39.392
ABORTION HERE IS STRICTLY

12:39.392 --> 12:40.493
ILLEGAL ALTHOUGH RARE EXCEPTIONS

12:40.493 --> 12:42.095
ARE MADE IF THE HEALTH OF THE

12:42.095 --> 12:44.163
MOTHER IS AT RISK.

12:44.163 --> 12:45.932
OUTSIDE THE VATICAN IT IS THE

12:45.932 --> 12:47.700
ONLY COUNTRY IN THE WORLD WHERE

12:47.700 --> 12:49.235
DIVORCE IS STILL NOT ALLOWED.

12:49.235 --> 12:50.536
AND WHILE THE PHILIPPINE CHURCH

12:50.536 --> 12:53.373
SAYS IT IS NOT OPPOSED TO

12:53.373 --> 12:55.174
NATURAL FAMILY PLANNING--

12:55.174 --> 12:56.342
AVOIDING INTERCOURSE WHEN A

12:56.342 --> 12:58.077
WOMAN IS MOST FERTILE-- IT

12:58.077 --> 12:59.679
REMAINS OPPOSED TO ALL FORMS OF

12:59.679 --> 13:06.052
ARTIFICIAL CONTRACEPTION.

13:06.052 --> 13:07.720
CONTRACEPTION IN THE EYES OF THE

13:07.720 --> 13:09.088
CHURCH IS STILL IMMORAL?

13:09.088 --> 13:10.690
>> YES.

13:10.690 --> 13:12.058
>> Reporter: YOU DO BELIEVE IT

13:12.058 --> 13:12.925
LEADS TO PROMISCUITY AMONG OTHER

13:12.925 --> 13:15.795
THINGS?

13:15.795 --> 13:18.264
>> YES.

13:18.264 --> 13:19.866
>> Reporter: IF THE PEOPLE OF

13:19.866 --> 13:21.067
THE PHILIPPINES ARE IN SUPPORT

13:21.067 --> 13:22.435
OF POPULATION CONTROL AND

13:22.435 --> 13:23.803
CONTRACEPTION, AND THEY WANT

13:23.803 --> 13:26.372
THEIR CHILDREN TO LEARN IN

13:26.372 --> 13:28.374
SCHOOL PROPER FAMILY PLANNING

13:28.374 --> 13:30.143
EDUCATION, WHY WOULD THE CHURCH

13:30.143 --> 13:34.514
OPPOSE ANY OF THAT?

13:34.514 --> 13:35.682
>> THE CHURCH PROMOTES

13:35.682 --> 13:38.384
PARENTHOOD.

13:38.384 --> 13:39.652
ONLY LET IT BE RESPONSIBLE

13:39.652 --> 13:41.087
PARENTHOOD.

13:41.087 --> 13:43.156
THE CHURCH HAS NEVER SAID, "GO

13:43.156 --> 13:46.859
AHEAD, MULTIPLY AS MUCH AS YOU

13:46.859 --> 13:47.794
LIKE OR THAT... AND LET THE GOOD

13:47.794 --> 13:49.395
LORD PROVIDE."

13:49.395 --> 13:50.797
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

13:50.797 --> 13:52.131
THE CHURCH PREACHES RESPONSIBLE

13:52.131 --> 13:54.267
PARENTHOOD THROUGH NATURAL

13:54.267 --> 13:58.438
FAMILY PLANNING.

13:58.438 --> 13:59.605
>> Reporter: BUT CHANGES ARE NOW

13:59.605 --> 14:01.007
UNDERWAY IN THE PHILIPPINES THAT

14:01.007 --> 14:01.908
COULD HELP SLOW THE POPULATION

14:01.908 --> 14:03.476
BOOM.

14:03.476 --> 14:05.044
THIS PAST SPRING, AFTER A 15-

14:05.044 --> 14:08.081
YEAR BATTLE THAT WENT ALL THE

14:08.081 --> 14:09.182
WAY TO THE FILIPINO SUPREME

14:09.182 --> 14:10.183
COURT, A NEW REPRODUCTIVE

14:10.183 --> 14:11.818
HEALTHCARE LAW TOOK EFFECT.

14:11.818 --> 14:13.152
IT REQUIRES THE PHILIPPINE

14:13.152 --> 14:15.221
GOVERNMENT TO FUND FAMILY

14:15.221 --> 14:16.656
PLANNING HEALTH CLINICS, PROVIDE

14:16.656 --> 14:18.324
AFFORDABLE CONTRACEPTION, AND

14:18.324 --> 14:19.525
LAUNCH COMPREHENSIVE SEX

14:19.525 --> 14:21.861
EDUCATION IN SCHOOLS.

14:21.861 --> 14:23.696
FORMER HEALTH SECRETARY CABRAL,

14:23.696 --> 14:27.433
ONE OF THE MOST PROMINENT

14:27.433 --> 14:29.068
SUPPORTERS OF THE NEW LAW, SAYS

14:29.068 --> 14:30.236
IT'S ABOUT TIME.

14:30.236 --> 14:31.437
>> IT'S A VICTORY FOR ALL

14:31.437 --> 14:32.605
FILIPINOS, ESPECIALLY WOMEN AND

14:32.605 --> 14:34.307
CHILDREN.

14:34.307 --> 14:36.876
THE LAW CAN MAKE A VERY BIG DENT

14:36.876 --> 14:39.445
IN OUR PROBLEM WITH POVERTY AND

14:39.445 --> 14:41.214
POPULATION.

14:41.214 --> 14:42.215
>> Reporter: SO IS THIS A DEFEAT

14:42.215 --> 14:44.083
FOR THE CATHOLIC CHURCH?

14:44.083 --> 14:45.852
>> I THINK SO.

14:45.852 --> 14:47.587
>> Reporter: THE FIGHT WENT ON

14:47.587 --> 14:49.255
FOR 15 YEARS AND, WITH ALL DUE

14:49.255 --> 14:50.456
RESPECT, ARCHBISHOP, THE CHURCH

14:50.456 --> 14:52.091
LOST.

14:52.091 --> 14:58.765
>> YES, YES-- WHAT'S NEW?

14:58.765 --> 15:00.099
THE CHURCH TEACHES, THE WORLD

15:00.099 --> 15:04.203
DOES NOT LISTEN.

15:04.203 --> 15:06.539
IF THE CHURCH TEACHES AND THE

15:06.539 --> 15:07.774
WORLD LISTENS, THAT WOULD BE A

15:07.774 --> 15:13.179
FIRST-CLASS MIRACLE.

15:13.179 --> 15:14.113
>> Reporter: BUT BEFORE THE BILL

15:14.113 --> 15:15.548
WAS IMPLEMENTED, THE CHURCH AND

15:15.548 --> 15:17.016
ITS SUPPORTERS WON SOME MAJOR

15:17.016 --> 15:19.018
CONCESSIONS FROM SUPREME COURT,

15:19.018 --> 15:20.720
EFFECTIVELY DILUTING THE LAW:

15:20.720 --> 15:22.488
PRIVATE HOSPITALS OWNED BY

15:22.488 --> 15:24.657
RELIGIOUS INSTITUTIONS WILL NOT

15:24.657 --> 15:25.925
HAVE TO PROVIDE FAMILY PLANNING

15:25.925 --> 15:27.960
OPTIONS OR EVEN REFER PATIENTS

15:27.960 --> 15:29.595
TO HOSPITALS THAT WILL PROVIDE

15:29.595 --> 15:31.364
THE SERVICES.

15:31.364 --> 15:32.532
MINORS SEEKING BIRTH CONTROL

15:32.532 --> 15:34.066
PILLS OR CONDOMS WILL REQUIRE

15:34.066 --> 15:36.702
PARENTAL CONSENT.

15:36.702 --> 15:38.504
AND MARRIED WOMEN WILL HAVE TO

15:38.504 --> 15:40.706
HAVE THEIR HUSBANDS CONSENT IF

15:40.706 --> 15:42.041
THEY WANT TO UNDERGO A FERTILITY

15:42.041 --> 15:46.646
PROCEDURE LIKE INSERTING AN IUD.

15:46.646 --> 15:47.847
>> OUR MAIN CONCERN IS THAT

15:47.847 --> 15:51.517
WE'RE LOOKING AT WOMEN AND YOUNG

15:51.517 --> 15:52.652
GIRLS HAVE THE RIGHT TO CHOOSE,

15:52.652 --> 15:53.519
YOU KNOW, FREELY AND

15:53.519 --> 15:54.687
RESPONSIBLY, THE NUMBER OF

15:54.687 --> 15:55.788
CHILDREN THEY WANT AND WHEN THEY

15:55.788 --> 15:57.156
WANT THEM.

15:57.156 --> 15:58.257
>> Reporter: KLAUS BECK IS THE

15:58.257 --> 15:59.258
HEAD OF THE UNITED NATIONS

15:59.258 --> 16:00.293
POPULATION FUND IN THE

16:00.293 --> 16:01.994
PHILIPPINES.

16:01.994 --> 16:03.229
WHILE HE CHEERS THE PASSAGE OF

16:03.229 --> 16:04.363
THE REPRODUCTIVE HEALTH CARE LAW

16:04.363 --> 16:06.132
HERE, HE SAYS THAT FOR THE LAW

16:06.132 --> 16:07.733
TO BE EFFECTIVE IT MUST EMPOWER

16:07.733 --> 16:12.171
WOMEN TO MAKE THEIR OWN CHOICES,

16:12.171 --> 16:13.039
WHICH THE CURRENT LAW NOW

16:13.039 --> 16:14.607
LIMITS.

16:14.607 --> 16:16.042
WITHOUT THOSE CHOICES MANY WOMEN

16:16.042 --> 16:17.276
MAY STILL FEEL THE NEED TO SEEK

16:17.276 --> 16:19.278
OUT ABORTIONS.

16:19.278 --> 16:21.280
HERE IN MANILA, THAT MEANS A

16:21.280 --> 16:24.817
VISIT TO WHAT COULD BE DESCRIBED

16:24.817 --> 16:25.785
AS AN ABORTION BLACK MARKET,

16:25.785 --> 16:27.353
RIGHT OUTSIDE THE 400-YEAR-OLD

16:27.353 --> 16:29.155
CHURCH OF THE BLACK NAZARENE.

16:29.155 --> 16:30.957
RIGHT ALONGSIDE THE ROSARY BEADS

16:30.957 --> 16:32.558
AND STATUES OF SAINTS,

16:32.558 --> 16:34.827
SHOPKEEPERS OPENLY OFFER A

16:34.827 --> 16:36.028
VARIETY OF HERBS AND POTIONS,

16:36.028 --> 16:37.630
PROMISING TO INDUCE MENSTRUATION

16:37.630 --> 16:38.898
AS A WAY TO END UNWANTED

16:38.898 --> 16:41.567
PREGNANCIES.

16:41.567 --> 16:42.935
FOR THE EQUIVALENT OF FIVE

16:42.935 --> 16:45.037
DOLLARS, WE WERE ABLE TO BUY

16:45.037 --> 16:47.840
THIS CONCOCTION-- WHAT THE

16:47.840 --> 16:48.908
VENDOR DESCRIBED AS AN HERBAL

16:48.908 --> 16:50.810
REMEDY, A BREW THAT'S SUPPOSED

16:50.810 --> 16:52.578
INDUCE MISCARRIAGES IN THE FIRST

16:52.578 --> 16:55.414
TRIMESTER OF PREGNANCY.

16:55.414 --> 16:56.983
OTHERS MAY FIND IT NECESSARY TO

16:56.983 --> 16:59.051
FIND SOMEONE IN THESE BACK

16:59.051 --> 17:02.321
ALLEYS TO PERFORM AN ABORTION.

17:02.321 --> 17:04.457
WE MET UP WITH A WOMAN CALLED

17:04.457 --> 17:05.224
ROSE WHO DID NOT WANT TO BE

17:05.224 --> 17:07.059
IDENTIFIED ON CAMERA.

17:07.059 --> 17:08.661
ROSE SAYS SHE HAS ASSISTED

17:08.661 --> 17:09.962
DOCTORS PERFORMING HUNDREDS OF

17:09.962 --> 17:13.666
ABORTIONS.

17:13.666 --> 17:14.700
>> EVERY DAY WE HAD THREE TO

17:14.700 --> 17:16.068
FIVE PATIENTS, BECAUSE IT WOULD

17:16.068 --> 17:17.336
ONLY TAKE 15 MINUTES FOR EACH

17:17.336 --> 17:20.573
PROCEDURE.

17:20.573 --> 17:22.808
>> Reporter: ACCORDING TO THE

17:22.808 --> 17:23.743
CENTER FOR REPRODUCTIVE RIGHTS

17:23.743 --> 17:25.444
THERE ARE MORE THAN 500,000

17:25.444 --> 17:26.646
ILLEGAL ABORTIONS IN THE

17:26.646 --> 17:27.980
PHILIPPINES EVERY YEAR.

17:27.980 --> 17:31.150
AN ESTIMATED 1,000 WOMEN DIE

17:31.150 --> 17:32.618
EVERY YEAR OF COMPLICATIONS FROM

17:32.618 --> 17:34.754
THOSE PROCEDURES.

17:34.754 --> 17:36.289
WHILE THE LIMITATIONS OF THE NEW

17:36.289 --> 17:37.723
REPRODUCTIVE HEALTH CARE LAW ARE

17:37.723 --> 17:39.525
CLEAR, FORMER HEALTH SECRETARY

17:39.525 --> 17:43.062
CABRAL IS OPTIMISTIC THAT IT

17:43.062 --> 17:44.530
WILL EVENTUALLY LOWER THE NUMBER

17:44.530 --> 17:45.998
OF UNWANTED PREGNANCIES AND

17:45.998 --> 17:47.633
EVENTUALLY SLOW THE POPULATION

17:47.633 --> 17:49.635
GROWTH.

17:49.635 --> 17:52.004
>> EVEN THOUGH THE PRAGMATIC

17:52.004 --> 17:53.940
PURPOSE OF THE BILL IS NOT

17:53.940 --> 17:55.408
POPULATION CONTROL, AS WE KNOW

17:55.408 --> 17:56.943
FROM OTHER COUNTRIES, IF YOU

17:56.943 --> 17:58.811
GIVE MOTHERS A CHANCE, WHAT

17:58.811 --> 17:59.979
ACTUALLY HAPPENS IS THE

17:59.979 --> 18:03.716
POPULATION RATES GO DOWN.

18:03.716 --> 18:06.319
>> Reporter: FOR CABRAL AND MANY

18:06.319 --> 18:07.920
OTHERS IN THE PHILIPPINES,

18:07.920 --> 18:09.155
FAILURE IS NOT AN OPTION.

18:09.155 --> 18:10.456
THE NEED TO CONTROL THIS

18:10.456 --> 18:11.724
COUNTRY'S POPULATION GROWTH IS

18:11.724 --> 18:13.125
BECOMING A MATTER OF SURVIVAL

18:13.125 --> 18:16.963
FOR FILIPINOS TODAY-- A MATTER

18:16.963 --> 18:18.464
OF SURVIVAL FROM THE CRADLE TO

18:18.464 --> 18:20.700
THOSE GRAVEYARDS, WHERE PEOPLE

18:20.700 --> 18:22.401
ARE NOW LIVING AS SQUATTERS,

18:22.401 --> 18:23.903
BECAUSE THEY HAVE NOWHERE ELSE

18:23.903 --> 18:31.110
TO LIVE.

18:31.110 --> 18:32.078
>> Sreenivasan: SEE MORE FROM

18:32.078 --> 18:33.179
ONE OF THE WORLD'S BUSIEST

18:33.179 --> 18:34.347
MATERNITY WARDS IN THE

18:34.347 --> 18:35.314
PHILIPPINES.

