VISIT NEWSHOUR.PBS.ORG.

18:36.882 --> 18:38.317
AS WE REPORTED YESTERDAY, THERE

18:38.317 --> 18:39.285
ARE NOW ARE MORE THAN 2,6OO

18:39.285 --> 18:40.386
CONFIRMED OR SUSPECTED CASES OF

18:40.386 --> 18:41.821
EBOLA AND MORE THAN 1,400 DEATHS

18:41.821 --> 18:43.456
RESULTING FROM THE VIRUS.

