NEIGHBORHOOD HERE, PEOPLE WERE

19:03.175 --> 19:04.543
STARTING TO FIGHT BACK AGAINST

19:04.543 --> 19:05.644
THE POLICE.

19:05.644 --> 19:08.214
HAVE TENSIONS EASED?

19:08.214 --> 19:09.482
>> Reporter: TENSIONS RIGHT NOW

19:09.482 --> 19:11.250
ARE A LITTLE BIT EASIER THAN

19:11.250 --> 19:13.185
THEY WERE A WHILE AGO BUT THE

19:13.185 --> 19:15.521
FUNDAMENTAL PROBLEM IN LIBERIA,

19:15.521 --> 19:17.289
ONE IS REALLY ONE OF GOVERNMENT

19:17.289 --> 19:18.224
MISTRUST IS STILL THERE.

