THERE IS A REAL GULF BETWEEN THE

19:25.798 --> 19:26.799
GOVERNED AND THE GOVERNMENT AND

19:26.799 --> 19:28.000
THE FUNDAMENTAL PROBLEM WHICH IS

19:28.000 --> 19:29.769
THAT PEOPLE THINK THAT EBOLA IS

