IN DAYS TO COME ESPECIALLY AS

19:45.384 --> 19:47.353
PEOPLE GET HUNGRY IN THE

19:47.353 --> 19:48.287
QUARANTINED NEIGHBORHOOD.

19:48.287 --> 19:51.157
>> THE FEAR SPREADS FASTER THAN

19:51.157 --> 19:53.893
THE VIRUS TO DOES.

19:53.893 --> 19:59.131
>> WHEN PEOPLE PANIC, THEY START

19:59.131 --> 20:00.266
DISBELIEVING PEOPLE THEY HAVE

20:00.266 --> 20:02.535
BELIEVED ALL THEIR LIVES, THEIR

20:02.535 --> 20:06.972
COMMUNITY LEADERS, HEALERS AND A

20:06.972 --> 20:08.207
COMMUNITY LEADER, DOESN'T HAVE

20:08.207 --> 20:10.843
AS MUCH SWAY WHEN THIS POPS UP

20:10.843 --> 20:11.610
IN THEIR NEIGHBORHOOD.

20:11.610 --> 20:13.979
>> DAVID, DO THE NEIGHBORS THERE

20:13.979 --> 20:15.614
HAVE A PLAN ESTABLISHED FOR IT,

20:15.614 --> 20:16.916
ARE THEY CALLING FOR OUTSIDE

20:16.916 --> 20:17.883
ASSISTANCE?

20:17.883 --> 20:19.418
>> THEY ARE THE FIRST TO TELL

20:19.418 --> 20:21.220
YOU THEY ARE MAKING THIS UP AS

20:21.220 --> 20:22.121
THEY GO ALONG.

20:22.121 --> 20:23.089
I THINK WHAT HAPPENED WAS IN

20:23.089 --> 20:27.326
APRIL THERE WAS A DIP AND

20:27.326 --> 20:28.527
EVERYONE THOUGHT OKAY THIS VIRUS

20:28.527 --> 20:29.795
HAS BURNED OUT.

